stories.title: South Africa enter Sharjah Cup final
stories.summary:
Sharjah, March 27: India came here with the reputation of being the
favourites

stories.title: Inconsistency has been the Indians' major problem
stories.summary: The Indians failed badly on the day of reckoning to be knocked out of the Coca-Cola Cup at Sharjah

stories.title: South Africa beat India, do Pakistan a favour
stories.summary:
South Africa made heavy weather of a modest target of 165 but held
their nerve to win a third successive match in the Coca Cola Cup and
their eighth in eight appearances at this venue
